STEP File Viewer - Section view clipping planes

The visualization was generated by the NIST STEP File Analyzer and Viewer. The STEP file was generated from one of the NIST CAD models. The graphical PMI is defined the STEP file. Key 'a' to view all, 'r' to restore, PageDown for viewpoints. Use the mouse in 'Examine Mode' to rotate, pan, zoom. More examples.
